I don’t know the whole story and only know anything because of YouTube recommendations as well as my 12 year old explaining what the Hype house was. I laughed so hard and haven’t stopped after a comment she made last night in regards to that Thomas kid when he said “it’s a mans world...”. I promise she’s a good kid but we definitely say silly things for shock value when in certain moods. She said “it’s a mans world is it? Well then that douche canoe can push a baby out his.....beep”. But it’s so freakin funny because she said “douche canoe” but then literally said the word “beep”. In fact she all but ran out of the room when I tried to get her to say the actual word.
Oh my gosh I’m a horrible momma!!!
